of: introduce of_dma_get_range() helper

The of_dma_get_range() allows to find "dma-range" property for
the specified device and parse it.
 dma-ranges format:
   DMA addr (dma_addr)          : naddr cells
   CPU addr (phys_addr_t)       : pna cells
   size                         : nsize cells

